{"tid":186432,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"5次劈炮自覺型 80後做老闆即鬧：呢一代唔受得氣","createTime":"2017-04-04T07:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T12:36:28.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":126,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf330e096c20c244de8057a383cdcc811f2c6d8","tid":186432,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:57:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>5次劈炮自覺型 80後做老闆即鬧：呢一代唔受得氣<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170404/2_494566_0/-%E8%A3%B8%E8%BE%AD%E9%81%94%E4%BA%BA-5%E6%AC%A1%E5%8A%88%E7%82%AE%E8%87%AA%E8%A6%BA%E5%9E%8B-80%E5%BE%8C%E5%81%9A%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E5%8D%B3%E9%AC%A7-%E5%91%A2%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E5%94%94%E5%8F%97%E5%BE%97%E6%B0%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170404%2F2_494566_0%2F-%25E8%25A3%25B8%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E9%2581%2594%25E4%25BA%25BA-5%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E5%258A%2588%25E7%2582%25AE%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A6%25BA%25E5%259E%258B-80%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2581%259A%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E5%258D%25B3%25E9%25AC%25A7-%25E5%2591%25A2%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25BE%2597%25E6%25B0%25A3&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iStzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=19a7029f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170404%2F2_494566_0%2F-%25E8%25A3%25B8%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E9%2581%2594%25E4%25BA%25BA-5%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E5%258A%2588%25E7%2582%25AE%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A6%25BA%25E5%259E%258B-80%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2581%259A%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E5%258D%25B3%25E9%25AC%25A7-%25E5%2591%25A2%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25BE%2597%25E6%25B0%25A3&h=0d33e145\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170404/2_494566_0/-%E8%A3%B8%E8%BE%AD%E9%81%94%E4%BA%BA-5%E6%AC%A1%E5%8A%88%E7%82%AE%E8%87%AA%E8%A6%BA%E5%9E%8B-80%E5%BE%8C%E5%81%9A%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E5%8D%B3%E9%AC%A7-%E5%91%A2%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E5%94%94%E5%8F%97%E5%BE%97%E6%B0%A3</a></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/875Cm5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F875Cm5e.png&h=d132974b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n近年網絡上出現「裸辭無罪」的呼聲，尤其在二十至三十歲的年齡層較為普遍；但隨着年齡增長，再談裸辭，又要負上甚麼代價？ <br />\n<br />\n八十後的Cruz是廚師，最近五份工皆是裸辭，對他來說如家常便飯。「細個係好囂架，我有才華，去到邊都請。」他大大小小的餐廳都做過，包括五星級香港W酒店、中環米芝蓮三星西餐廳。「辭職都係頂唔順公司制度或老闆要求。」他帶點自豪地說。 <br />\n<br />\nCruz的裸辭故事類同：有次一名意大利總廚認為他的烹調方式不稱心，竟二話不說衝到Cruz面前，一手搶走煎鍋丟到垃圾桶，「好侮辱！炒完午餐，一脫圍裙我就走，好型。」又一次，於上海一間高級西餐廳做廚師，老闆是香港人，經常亂買食材來叫他煮，Cruz打了個比喻：「我米芝蓮三星，你俾翠華叉燒我？大閘蟹、年糕？係咪玩我？」 <br />\n<br />\n這次，他放棄了一份三萬八千元人民幣月薪的三年合約，包括複式兩層的員工住宿單位及所有車錢和伙食費，「返到香港實搵到第二份，而且嗰時後生，無諗咁長遠。」 <br />\n<br />\nCruz不想受氣，最終決定自己做老闆，兩個月前在旺角開設一間西餐廳，角色互換後即時指摘年輕一代「唔受得氣」，「我好彩啫，你都要食飯架？如果你行得出嚟個社會，咪接受一下社會囉。而家呢一代，唔係好受得氣。除非你盡晒力做好自己，咁就絕對歡迎。」"},{"pid":"976cf314c8240173b97dd604190e9ec5ef574089","tid":186432,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:02:41.000Z","msg":"自己唔受氣就得<br />\n其他人唔受氣就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f0fc31869d7db05cac69ec1b6a62d164eba326","tid":186432,"uid":42367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:05:03.000Z","msg":"香港打工文化最緊要無錢都要ot包埋做出氣袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e2ac38ee9335c165cef2b3e27a303777dcc952","tid":186432,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T08:05:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64978a3f07ff3082626a3d02432b2b0a63dbd29","tid":186432,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited